# Session start

1. Read `HANDOFF.md` first
2. Read `PLATFORM-GUIDE.md` (rules, modules, launch checklist)
3. Read `README.md` sections only when needed
4. Work on one module per session
5. State which build-priority item the task serves

# Before each action

Consult `HANDOFF.md`, then `PLATFORM-GUIDE.md`, then `README.md` sections when needed.

# After each action

Update `HANDOFF.md` **Live session state** after every completed action. Append `README.md` Ordered Build Record once per session/milestone. Read README **sections** only — not the whole file every time — see `PLATFORM-GUIDE.md` Completion standard.

# Session end

1. Run `npm run lint && npm run type-check && npm run test`
2. Commit and push to GitHub
3. Update `HANDOFF.md` live session state and session log
4. Append `README.md` Ordered Build Record if behavior changed

# Handoff rule

Never switch between Cursor and Codex with uncommitted work. Update `HANDOFF.md` first.
